snippet.title: Cory in the Ded 3.5 - Game Debut
snippet.description:
PLAY THE GAME NOW!!!!! GRAAH!!!! https://sonicfangameshq.com/forums/showcase/cory-in-the-ded-3-5-sage-2022-demo.1456/

It's the ultimate Cory in the Ded celebration! Radfordhound returns in a new 2D platforming high speed adventure, and he's not alone! Far from it, in fact! 

Developed in collaboration between BriceTAS, BriceTAS, BriceTAS, and Autumn who made the trailer, experience new zones and remixed classic levels with Radfordhound, Dankles, Tails, Cas, Claire, Sanok, Autumn, Lucky, and GPF!

MUSIC CREDITS: 

"Checkpoint" 
Performed by NITRO FUN & HYPER POTIONS; Words and Music by Gustavo Rangel, Kevin Villecco, Ian Tsuchiura
